  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dd6\u0db4\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dbd\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Another person who broke into the television was arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Another suspect, who was wanted by the police, has been arrested in connection with the incident of forced entry to the National Television. The suspect was arrested after surrendering to the Colombo Kurunduwatta Police."
      ],
